Package: socratr
Type: Package
Title: Fast R Interface to Socrata Open Data Portals
Description: Read, write, and list datasets on Socrata open data portals
    <https://dev.socrata.com>. Fetches data via the SODA 3 POST query API
    with automatic pagination, and supports parallel fetching and uploading
    for large datasets. Converts dates to 'POSIX' format and manages
    throttling. Inspired by the RSocrata package
    <https://github.com/Chicago/RSocrata> by the City of Chicago.
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2025-04-15
Authors@R: person("Derek Schaadt", email = "dschaadt@alum.mit.edu",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
